title: Occupations - Peddlers - Christmas trees.

text:
Peddlers, Christmas Trees: A set of 3 views of trees for the Christmas trade piled in the center of West Street. The photographers vantage point is at Duane Street (No. 1); and Chambers Street (Nos. 2 and 3).
